{"tid":1059914,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"為 Pixel 3 XL 植入 Windows 系統 已成功開啟 Console 視窗","createTime":"2019-03-13T12:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T09:09:38.000Z","uid":50534,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22d20cae310e645fbe2e8e3556135fa86d8cea71","tid":1059914,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:07:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/12/pixel-3-xl-windows-10/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2Fpixel-3-xl-windows-10%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=30c8db2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/12/pixel-3-xl-windows-10/mobile-phone/</a><br />\n以往很多開發者都會將遊戲《DOOM》移植到其他裝置視為挑戰，現在門檻似乎已經大大提高，開發者喜歡將 Windows 10 系統安裝到各種裝置，例如陳舊的 Lumia 950 手機、Raspberry Pi 微型電腦或最近的任天堂 Switch 主機，而網民 NTAuthority 則選擇了 Pixel 3 XL 手機。<br />\n<br />\n來源：NTAuthority<br />\n<br />\n他日前在個人 Twitter 帳號上載了影片，展示他成功在 Google Pixel 3 XL 載入 Windows 10 的畫面。相信他選擇了 Windows 10 ARM 版系統，所以能夠在這部使用 ARM 架構處理器的 Android 手機運行，影片可見手機展示 Windows 10 的系統介面載入的畫面，然後打開了 Console 視窗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/0312-5a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F0312-5a.gif&h=47ece910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：NTAuthority<br />\n<br />\n現時開發還在初期階段，距離能夠正式使用還有一段距離，如果要讓 Windows 10 充分利用 Pixel 3 XL 的硬件，將需要大量驅動程式的配合。"},{"pid":"375f7b8ec28dcced3b91b7514eae942a1b628de0","tid":1059914,"uid":16208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a200fcdba2e1f536bf05fc86165fa01266c30909","tid":1059914,"uid":39305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 又搞得差<br />\n<br />\nApple 又唔想移植落iOS device"},{"pid":"beb7dd1671af3f56f6b2111855e729f6d56f7077","tid":1059